  "title": "Service staff",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Summary</strong></h3><p>The Waiter / Waitress is responsible for providing friendly and efficient service to customers, ensuring a pleasant dining experience from order taking to payment.</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Greet and seat customers in a polite and friendly manner</p></li><li><p>Take food and beverage orders accurately</p></li><li><p>Serve food and drinks according to service standards</p></li><li><p>Ensure tables are clean, properly set, and ready for customers</p></li><li><p>Respond promptly to customer requests and enquiries</p></li><li><p>Handle billing and payment transactions when required</p></li><li><p>Maintain cleanliness of dining area and service stations</p></li><li><p>Follow hygiene, safety, and service procedures</p></li><li><p>Work closely with kitchen and service team to ensure smooth operations</p></li></ul>",
